        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/35072101/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u35072101-5.jpg" alt="春诵夏弦" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12972525/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12972525/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/35072101/" class=" " title="春诵夏弦">春诵夏弦</a>
              
                <span class="allstar10" title="很差"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12972525">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">原著是经典，但看看作者名字的翻译就知道译者的斤两了。</span>
